{
  "stem": "6845.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we always had a carriage, but we didn't have the horse.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So if somebody came special, then we would rent a horse and somebody who would ride the carriage with the horse.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we had a cow by the name of Rose, because my mother believed in it that it's very important.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The milk should be really of the best quality for the children.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we had our own cow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And consequently, when it was Jewish holidays, we would go into the city of Uzhorod, which was about 14 kilometers or 10 kilometers-- I'm not to good with this, to remember.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Anyway, the cow came with us along the road, and behind the carriage.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And when we got there, of course, they had to-- we made arrangements for the cow.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But she was very unhappy and was making lots of noise.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And my grandfather, where we-- with whom we spent the holidays, complained quite a bit that, if this cow cannot be more or better adjusted, she shouldn't come into the city.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "She should just stay out in the countryside, in Sobrance.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But my mother insisted.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We always had the cow with us, and the holidays were very pleasant.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the school was also very pleasant.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Everybody knew everyone.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was just over a thousand people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I will tell you highlights.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "For example, my mother insisted I should learn the piano from an early age.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And so, it was the principal's son who was the piano teacher, and he taught me for six years.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And after six years, he walked up to my mother and says, madam, I don't think I want to take your money any longer.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Your daughter is a-- a hopeless case.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So that was my piano learning experience.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
